	(mips_n64_exec_plt0_entry, mips_exec_plt_entry): New tables.
	(mips_elf_link_hash_newfunc): Update after the changes to
	mips_elf_link_hash_entry.
	(mips_elf_check_mips16_stubs): Replace the DATA parameter with
